subject: Good morning,
body:
Good morning,  
How are you doing today, hope you are fine please i have something to
tell you. If you don't mind.
Am waiting for your response.
Bast regards.
Richard Godwin. Thanks.

subject: Re:   Good morning,
body:
Hello Richard Godwin,

Good morning to you too! I'm doing well, thank you for asking. I hope you're having a great day as well. 

I'm all ears for what you have to share. Please feel free to tell me.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Gladys
